@node "AmyBW" "AmyBW"

 AmyBW is a freeware BlueWave and QWK mailreader created by Leon
 Makkink. The latest version, and last :(, is 2.14. You can find
 it on Aminet.

@endnode

@node "QBlue" "QBlue"

 QBlue is a shareware BlueWave and QWK mailreader created by Paul
 Kienitz. The latest version (and last) is 2.0. It can be found on
 Aminet.

@endnode

